  %% Diagram 82: Self-Funding Gates and External Funding Decision Tree

  Start[Start self-funding path]
  G1[Gate 1 Month 4\n20 vendors target]
  G2[Gate 2 Month 6\nFirst 50K revenue month]
  G3[Gate 3 Month 9\n100 vendors and 150K revenue]
  G4[Gate 4 Month 12\n500 vendors and 350K revenue]
  G5[Gate 5 Month 15\nPublic launch and 500K+ revenue]

  E1{Gate 1 met?}
  E2{Gate 2 met?}
  E3{Gate 3 met?}
  E4{Gate 4 met?}
  E5{Gate 5 met?}

  Continue[Continue self-funded execution]
  Allocate[Allocate resources for next growth stage]
  External[Evaluate external funding option]
  Pivot[Pivot/cost control plan]

  Start --> G1 --> E1
  E1 -- Yes --> Continue --> Allocate --> G2 --> E2
  E2 -- Yes --> Continue --> Allocate --> G3 --> E3
  E3 -- Yes --> Continue --> Allocate --> G4 --> E4
  E4 -- Yes --> Continue --> Allocate --> G5 --> E5
  E5 -- Yes --> Continue

  E1 -- No --> Pivot --> External
  E2 -- No --> Pivot --> External
  E3 -- No --> Pivot --> External
  E4 -- No --> Pivot --> External
  E5 -- No --> Pivot --> External
